content: So as of yesterday, I believe the physical occupancy here at the end of April 94.6% in the same-store pool, which is I think the same 10 yet – the same 10 basis points difference to last year’s 94.7%, same 10 basis points as we would have experienced at the end of March. Ki, your line is open. Ki, your line is open. But even when you compare it to 2019, up 31%, I think that’s actually down a little bit when you compare to rate growth versus ‘19.
